            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x44983FFB<!--String: "Welcome to Outdoor Kids Camp! A place to build friendships, new skills, and unforgettable memories, plus plenty of outdoor activities and splashy good times! Each day brings a mix of main camp activities and role activities, which can be viewed or adjusted anytime from the top-left panel in Live Mode. Rest assured, the Camp Director and Camp Counselors are here to keep things running smoothly, guide the fun, and look after those mischievous little campers. Follow the plan or break away for an adventure, the outcome still brings special rewards based on how the Getaway unfolds!\n\nIf you want to learn more about everything Getaways has to offer, check out the lessons by selecting below!"--></T>
