              <T n="single">0x93E0DA8<!--String: "Welcome to Fitness Retreat, where muscles meet mindfulness! Sims will push their limits with heart-pumping workouts, dive into splashy outdoor fun, and recharge with moments of relaxation in between. Each day brings a mix of main activities and role activities, which can be viewed or adjusted anytime from the top-left panel in Live Mode. Switch things up, add new Roles, or remix the daily schedule to keep it fresh!\n\nIf you want to learn more about everything Getaways has to offer, check out the lessons by selecting below!"--></T>
