            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0xE13D71CA<!--String: "Love is in the air...along with a few surprises! Romantic Getaway promises sparks, chemistry, and maybe even a hot tub rendezvous, but with Romantic Elimination active, one Sim will be packing up at 11 AM each day. To stay in the game, Sims will need to turn on the charm and keep those romantic connections alive. Each day is filled with a mix of main activities and role activities, which can be viewed or adjusted anytime from the top-left panel in Live Mode. Change things up by editing the schedule or add new Sims to keep the drama spicy. And don't forget! The Romance Hosts will be around to cook, mingle, and stir the pot. After all, it's their house.\n\nIf you want to learn more about everything Getaways has to offer, check out the lessons by selecting below!"--></T>
